<P>
TALKING ABOUT DRUGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Thank you for the Commentary by Steven B. Duke (Dec. 21) in which he 
encourages the discussion of legalizing all drugs, because we are simply not 
going to ever, ever win a "war on drugs." 
</P>
<P>
 PHILIP CURTIS 
</P>
<P>
