<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Sunset League games: 
</P>
<P>
 Huntington Beach 61, Edison 58 -- Jenna Schnaker scored 17 points and Monica 
Geraci added 16 points and 11 rebounds to lead Huntington Beach (5-5, 1-0). 
Marie Philman scored 17 for No. 8 Edison (9-3, 0-1). 
