<P>
9TH ALGERIAN JUDGE KILLED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 An armed group killed the presiding judge of a court in western Algeria on 
Tuesday, the ninth magistrate slain since attacks attributed to Islamic 
radicals escalated in May. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
