 Newbury Park 53, Westlake 42 -- Jann Thorpe (15 points, 14 rebounds) led four 
Panthers in double figures in a Marmonte League opener. Julie Wastell (12 
points), Kara McKeown (11 points, 10 rebounds) and Amy Berman (11 points) also 
helped. Westlake's Shannon Sincock scored 18. 
</P>
<P>
 Simi Valley 49, Camarillo 38 -- The Pioneers (9-5) made 12 of 16 free throws 
in the fourth quarter in a Marmonte League opener. Sara Griffin had 17 points 
and 15 rebounds. Camarillo's Alisa Schmidt scored 16. 
</P>
