 Thousand Oaks 50, Agoura 26 -- Sara Samimi scored 15 points for Thousand Oaks 
(9-4, 1-0) in a Marmonte League opener at Agoura. 
</P>
<P>
 Bell-Jeff 74, Serra 33 -- Cathy Flores had 20 points and Christina Ticsay had 
24 for the Guards (10-3) in a Camino Real League opener. Carrie Breedlove had 
12 points, 15 rebounds and 10 blocked shots. 
</P>
