 Notre Dame 59, Chaminade 42 -- Valery Brady scored 22 points and Maggie Dixon 
added 16 points and 14 rebounds for the Knights (8-4) in a Mission League 
opener. 
</P>
<P>
 Nordhoff 58, St. Bonaventure 45 -- Rachel McSorley had 24 points and 12 
rebounds for Nordhoff (11-3) in a nonleague game at St. Bonaventure. Alisa 
Doran led the Seraphs with 22 points. 
</P>
<P>
 Hart 46, Burbank Burroughs 27 -- Jaime Broneer scored 10 points and La Cresha 
Clark added 10 rebounds and eight assists for Hart (10-6, 2-0) in a Foothill 
League game. Chrissy Russell led Burroughs (11-3, 1-1) with 13 points. 
</P>
<P>
 Oak Park 71, Moorpark 42 -- Bethany Goad had 13 points, Alexa Valavanis 12 and 
Natalie Davis 11 and nine rebounds for Oak Park. 
</P>
<P>
 Alemany 87, Harvard-Westlake 28 -- Carly Funicello scored 22 points and 
Samantha Rigley had 20 for Alemany (12-0) in a Mission League opener. GIRLS' 
SOCCER 
</P>
