<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: MISCELLANY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 There will be a memorial Thursday in Laguna Hills for Bob O'Leary, a former UC 
Irvine men's soccer assistant coach, college All-American and professional 
player who died Dec. 30 of cancer.He was 40. 
</P>
<P>
 The service will be at 6:30 p.m. at St. Nicholas Catholic Church, 24252 El 
Toro Road, Laguna Hills. Contributions can be made to the Pateadores "Bob 
O'Leary" Scholarship Fund, 26861 Trabuco Road, Suite E-217, Mission Viejo, 
92691. 
</P>
