<DATE>
<P>
January 5, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 6; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
