FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Movie ranking -- The 20th Century Fox release "Ghost in the Machine" ranked 
No. 10 on the list of top-grossing films for New Year's weekend, but was 
omitted from the box-office chart in Tuesday's Calendar. Its holiday weekend 
gross was $1.8 million. 
</P>
